{"word":"G4205 - πόρνος - pórnos - por'-nos - Fornicator","slug":"G4205","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πόρνος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pórnos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>por'-nos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fornicator"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - pornos</b> - <i>por'-nos</i><p/>From <b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BD;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>perne&#x0304;mi</b> (to <i>sell</i>; akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G4097\">G4097</a>); a (male) <i>prostitute</i> (as <i>venal</i>), that is, (by analogy) a <i>debauchee</i> (<i>libertine</i>): - fornicator, whoremonger."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1608\">G1608</a>, <a href=\"#/G4202\">G4202</a>, <a href=\"#/G4203\">G4203</a>, <a href=\"#/G4204\">G4204</a>"}]}